Because jColibri framework is built with java 1.6, you need to install old version for running CocktailCBR.
java 1.6 framework : 
http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/java-archive-downloads-javase6-419409.html

XMLToLinear is built on the newest version of java, for running you need to install the newer version than 1.8.
java 1.8 framework :
http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html

How to run CocktailCBR:
1. click CocktailCBR.bat

How to run XMLToLinear:
1. click XMLToLinear.bat
